description: So I was going through my phone deleting photos and came across pics of me last year when Covid did not exist and all the outings and events I got to go to 😫😭 legit every time I knew I had an event it always motivated me to stick to diet and exercise 😅 so this year I’ve been all over the place with consistency. Hopefully this all ends soon so I can have an excuse to dress up again and have a fancy night out in Melbourne 🙏🏽🔥 we were supposed to have our HUF end of challenge event in March and I full on bought an outfit. Now it’s just sitting in my wardrobe collecting dust. Lord help us lol #precovid#2019memories#outfits#bestyear#livinglife#missgoingout#homeworkout#gymgarage#plandemic2020#whenwillthisend#gains#love#
